is variant of the program can be installed in a desktop or a laptop computer, and analog signals from any gas chromatograph can be sent to the analog inputs of the }{\b Integrator}{. There are also several digital input and output lines at the }{\b 
Integrator}{ that allow a handshaking between the }{\b Integrator}{ and the Gas Chromatograph.  The }{\b WPEAK Computing Integrator}{ performs data acquisition, processing, displaying, and storing the results to the hard drive of the PC. 
